            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgCaralPiramideH1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgCaralPiramideH1', '0%')\" src=\"images/Caral/CaralPiramideH1.jpg\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 4</b>: Pyramid H1 in the archaeological site of Caral (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('720f6dfd-4b86-4e07-a887-1010e1041a4d'); return false;\">Ruta Caral, <htdate0></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('03c3743c-d268-4730-ba8e-d36b5c49e781'); return false;\">Youtube - Caral Perú Oficial, <htdate1></a>). Photo taken on <htdate2>, during a visit to the site.</p>",
